Mikaila https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mikaila 0 Mikaila Dominique Enriquez (born December 15, 1986), known as Mikaila, is an American former pop singer and former child actress from Edmond, Oklahoma. She is of French, Spanish and Native Mexican descent.
